        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        .font-heading {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="h-full overflow-auto bg-gray-50 flex flex-col">
    <!-- Header -->
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <!-- Content -->
    <main class="flex-grow w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 md:py-16">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 mb-12">
            <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8 uppercase tracking-wide font-semibold">Last Updated: February 2026</p>

            <div class="prose prose-blue max-w-none text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-8">
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
                    <p>We collect personal information such as your name, email address, phone number, PAN, Aadhaar, and
                        financial documents when you use our services. This information is necessary for tax filing and
                        compliance.</p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
                    <p>Your data is used solely for the purpose of preparing and filing your income tax returns,
                        communicating with you regarding your filing status, and providing customer support. We do not
                        sell your data to third parties.</p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. Data Security</h2>
                    <p>We implement industry-standard security measures, including encryption and secure servers, to
                        protect your personal and financial information from unauthorized access, alteration,
                        disclosure, or destruction.</p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Sharing of Information</h2>
                    <p>We may share your information with government tax authorities (e.g., Income Tax Department) as
                        required by law for filing purposes. We may also share data with trusted service providers who
                        assist us in operating our website, conducting our business, or serving our users.</p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
                    <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information held by us. If you
                        wish to exercise these rights, please contact our support team.</p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                    <p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting
                        the new Privacy Policy on this page.</p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    
    <script src="js/script.js"></script>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>